{"tid":384854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我數學差 求數學達人教我點寫羅馬數字4","createTime":"2017-09-02T16:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T17:33:14.000Z","uid":22440,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95be468da42967c55263a093a9a6863f97f1baa0","tid":384854,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"話說我啱啱同我屋企人討論關於羅馬數字問題啦<br />\n我地講到羅馬數字其實好反智的一種記數方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為4 係IV 5係V 6係VI<br />\n都唔明點解要咁麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為IV VI真係好易寫錯又難記 細個老師日日教我要背唯有係死背lor<br />\n之後講講下 我老母話：咩啊，4唔係四條直線咩<br />\n有幾難記啊 搵黎講<br />\n我話： 不可能 我細個背果堆咩黎嫁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後拎隻手錶黎對質<br />\n<br />\n竟然發現真係四條直線IIII ......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁其實我係唔係真係記錯 定係呢種係傳說中曼德拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無數學好人士指點<br />\n有無數學差人士背過"},{"pid":"b80002d0bf9a221102d9dbbeb36e574a0898d5d7","tid":384854,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"推 總是覺得好唔順眼 <br />\n總係覺得我無記錯"},{"pid":"771144e31db93fb4fddd8791fc2b96d609b52330","tid":384854,"uid":107013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"亖"},{"pid":"7465fc157948e3cb49bea36d59d08338c570cc2b","tid":384854,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"兩個都可以 IV比較正規"},{"pid":"c52dca9d355502f1782d99d9feee8d542bdf8a27","tid":384854,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:28:53.000Z","msg":"我係咁記<br />\nIV即係5之前一個數<br />\nVI即係5之後一個數<br />\n<br />\n好似行幾步路咁<br />\nV I I I<br />\n5678<br />\n<br />\n我都知好似簡單複雜化<br />\n利申數渣"},{"pid":"033e7f88e81691f31cd5a2c03872eb50e749e8ea","tid":384854,"uid":13181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"又曼德拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da59d621ecef9c262bbb34a31b07d41c41501f37","tid":384854,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又曼德拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實係信美觀論<br />\n因為我想肯定IV係存在<br />\n鐘唔鐘 錶唔錶唔係重點 <br />\n重點係究竟可唔可以咁寫"},{"pid":"f6eb04b133ab5d78db1891415be36e2315bfe4fa","tid":384854,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係咁記<br />\nIV即係5之前一個數<br />\nVI即係5之後一個數<br />\n<br />\n好似行幾步路咁<br />\nV I I I<br />\n5678<br />\n<br />\n我都知好似簡單複雜化<br />\n利申數渣</blockquote><br />\n我細個數學老師教I II III IV因為痴住前面一條條V係5 咁樣背lor"},{"pid":"8502aad789d45b5ab454af7d7d490b1f4cb029b7","tid":384854,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個都可以 IV比較正規</blockquote><br />\n姐係其實IV咁寫先係正規教科書教果種？"},{"pid":"2d9d6b73d4dd7e9c1c91f1813f57b56ce83afb07","tid":384854,"uid":100145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"IV方便D用，當個數去到好大嘅時候用IIII嗰種方法好難計返出黎，例如20,你唔會用20個I / VVVV,用XX會容易睇D"},{"pid":"f3e3eaa83eb2d1d8fcb66b802c3df9cb3aceb281","tid":384854,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩個都可以 IV比較正規</blockquote><br />\n姐係其實IV咁寫先係正規教科書教果種？</blockquote><br />\n講多少少<br />\n以古羅馬一開始係I II III IIII V<br />\nIV算係簡寫，好似cannot 同can't 既分別<br />\nVIIII 就簡寫成IX<br />\n咁經過年代變遷，IIII 同VIIII反而越黎越少人用，IV 同IX變左主流"},{"pid":"9b9c6221a9b86fd09cb5de55c427505e49815cd7","tid":384854,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係咁記<br />\nIV即係5之前一個數<br />\nVI即係5之後一個數<br />\n<br />\n好似行幾步路咁<br />\nV I I I<br />\n5678<br />\n<br />\n我都知好似簡單複雜化<br />\n利申數渣</blockquote><br />\n巴打呢個比喻好有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5818f2887b22765c75802c11d61271e05359ad","tid":384854,"uid":68483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:55:31.000Z","msg":"咩撚野手錶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47b533b8067f969044afa8001b1638a79fb7612","tid":384854,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩撚野手錶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手錶黎講，勞力士已經係用IIII，仲有好多唔同牌子都係用IIII，原因好似係因為感覺古典啲"},{"pid":"a7560f56bc982f5698a60d575977046680e4a4aa","tid":384854,"uid":32826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"IV係 1(I)喺前面5(V)喺後面<br />\nVI係 5(V)喺前面1(I)喺後面<br />\n<br />\n細喺前面係減<br />\n即係5-1=4<br />\n<br />\n大喺前面係加<br />\n即係5+1=6"},{"pid":"23cd8a8ef35e34ef2ae79a0b496255b5b8c163e8","tid":384854,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:33:14.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}